data.description: Location, location, location!! Newly renovated home in Hempfield school district to call your own! The entire first floor of this home has been remodeled in the last few months, featuring new luxury vinyl plank flooring spanning the entire first floor! A newly updated kitchen that includes upgraded counter tops and backslash tiling. Not to mention the spacious family room just off of the kitchen complete with a cozy wood burning fireplace! From the family room step out onto the brand new composite deck or spend a relaxing day in the pool. All from the comfort of your own backyard! Don't wait, schedule an appointment to see this spectacular home today!!
